- In our case, `B` is `toBoundedBilin ha 1 (i.indicator 1)`
- So `continuousLinearMapOfBilin (toBoundedBilin ha 1 (i.indicator 1))` is the map `x ↦ ∫ (i.indicator 1) z ∂(cfc_toComplexMeasure ha x x) z`

