2. We have a function `f : C((spectrum ℂ a), ℂ)`.
3. We have a set `i : Set ↑(spectrum ℂ a)`.
4. We assume `¬MeasurableSet i`.
5. We need to prove `continuousLinearMapOfBilin (@toBoundedBilin H inst✝² inst✝¹ inst✝ a ha 1 (i.indicator 1)) = 0`.

