I'll complete the proof of the theorem `toResolutionOfIdentity` in Lean 4. The goal is to show that for any non-measurable set `i`, the continuous linear map `continuousLinearMapOfBilin` applied to the bounded bilinear form `toBoundedBilin` with the indicator function `i.indicator 1` is zero.

